title: The Babysitter Killing: Episode 01
description:
In this edition of the UK True Crime Podcast we take a detailed look at the disturbing murder of Katie Wynter on Boxing Day 2011.  Katie was only 19 years old.

Teenager Katie had been deceived by the her boyfriend, Tony Bushby,  through an elaborate Facebook socal media campaign to increase his credibibility

In this edition of the UKTrueCrime podcast we examine how Tony Bushby deceived Katie and how he eventually stabbed her to death.
